<paragraph base="SL33273" principles="no" id="IAS39_72"><paranum>72</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 39"/><data name="paranum" value="72"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS39_P0480">This Standard does not restrict the circumstances in which a <xref base="SL134592" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_APPA.dita#IFRS09_APPA/IFRS09_DI0008" scope="local">derivative<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0086"/></ph></xref> may be designated as a <xref base="SL134657" href="IAS39_9_hedge-accounting.dita#IAS39_9_hedge-accounting/IAS39_P0210" scope="local">hedging instrument<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0167"/></ph></xref> provided the conditions in <xref base="A39-253" href="IAS39_88.dita#IAS39_88" id="IAS39_X0451">paragraph 88</xref> are met, except for some written options (see <xref base="F16147192" href="IAS39_AG94.dita#IAS39_AG94" id="IAS39_X0452">Appendix A paragraph AG94</xref>). However, a non&#x2011;derivative <xref base="SL147175" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0069">financial asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0123"/></ph></xref> or non&#x2011;derivative <xref base="SL147195" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0085">financial liability<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0127"/></ph></xref> may be designated as a hedging instrument only for a hedge of a foreign <xref base="SL144810" href="../ifrs07/IFRS07_APPA.dita#IFRS07_APPA/IFRS07_P0864">currency risk<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0066"/></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>